              "free_text": [
                " The systematic uncertainty. In the final",
                "result it is caused by the detector efficiency, which",
                "depends on a good knowledge of the spectra accepted and",
                "rejected by the coincidence system. The efficiency was",
                "calibrated with the 11B(p,gamma)12C reaction at proton",
                "energies stepped in such a way that the gamma ray to",
                "the 12C ground state would overlap with the gamma ray",
                "to 12C*(4.43 MeV) at the next higher proton energy."
              ]
            }
